WEBVTT

00:00:08.233 --> 00:00:10.000
Nanbu: DON'T LEAN
TOO FAR FORWARD.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.000
NOT TOO FAR BACK, EITHER.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.566
( Aragaki grunting )

00:00:13.566 --> 00:00:16.033
Nanbu: SPLIT YOUR WEIGHT
EVENLY, 50‐50.

00:00:16.033 --> 00:00:19.200
THAT'S THE FORM YOU NEED TO
PRACTICE UNTIL IT'S NATURAL...

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:21.600
FOR TOMORROW.

00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:27.766
WE'RE DOING THIS
FOR TOMORROW, ARAGAKI.

00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:30.266
( crowd cheering )

00:00:30.266 --> 00:00:33.600
‐ ( Joe gasping )
‐ Computer: TWO, THREE,

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:37.466
‐ FOUR, FIVE...
‐ ( Nanbu gasping )

00:00:37.466 --> 00:00:40.333
Aragaki: THERE'S A LOT TO
MAKE UP FOR, THINGS I'VE LOST,

00:00:40.333 --> 00:00:43.333
SO IT'S TIME YOU PAID
YOUR PART OF THE DEBT IN FULL.

00:00:43.333 --> 00:00:45.133
‐ ( Nanbu growls )
‐ Computer: NINE...

00:00:45.133 --> 00:00:46.966
Nanbu: HUH?

00:00:46.966 --> 00:00:48.833
( crowd cheering )

00:00:48.833 --> 00:00:50.200
Sachio: JOE!

00:00:52.133 --> 00:00:53.733
Joe: HEY, WHO ARE
YOU LOOKING AT?

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.900
I'M THE ONE YOU GOTTA BEAT HERE.

00:00:57.900 --> 00:00:59.933
DID YOU FORGET?

00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.706
♪

00:01:13.006 --> 00:01:14.940
( singing in Japanese )

00:02:29.580 --> 00:02:30.180
( overlapping chatter )

00:02:32.180 --> 00:02:33.646
( overlapping chatter )

00:02:33.646 --> 00:02:35.480
♪

00:02:39.646 --> 00:02:40.713
Man: KICK HIS ASS, ARAGAKI!

00:02:40.713 --> 00:02:42.713
Man #2: PUT HIM OUT
OF HIS MISERY, WILL YOU?

00:02:42.713 --> 00:02:44.246
Sachio: POPS, ISN'T THERE
SOMETHING JOE CAN DO?

00:02:44.246 --> 00:02:45.913
YOU TRAINED ARAGAKI, DIDN'T YOU?

00:02:45.913 --> 00:02:49.246
YOU SHOULD KNOW HIS WEAKNESSES
LIKE THE BACK OF YOUR HAND.

00:02:49.246 --> 00:02:51.146
Nanbu: I FIGURED
THIS WOULD HAPPEN.

00:02:51.146 --> 00:02:53.080
ARAGAKI'S PUSHED
HIS MEGALO‐BOXING

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.713
UP TO A WHOLE NEW LEVEL.

00:02:54.713 --> 00:02:57.246
LOOK AT THE SPRING OF
HIS PROSTHETICS IN HIS FOOTWORK.

00:02:59.113 --> 00:03:00.886
HE MIGHT NOT HAVE
A TON OF POWER,

00:03:00.886 --> 00:03:02.486
BUT HE CAN SEND COUNTERS FLYING

00:03:02.486 --> 00:03:04.253
AS SOON AS HIS OPPONENT'S
FINISHED PUNCHING HIM.

00:03:09.986 --> 00:03:12.853
JOE, THERE MIGHT BE
NO WAY TO WIN THIS.

00:03:16.253 --> 00:03:18.220
Man #1: HEY,
WE CAME TO SEE A FIGHT!

00:03:18.220 --> 00:03:21.520
THIS IS NO TIME
FOR A SLOW DANCE!

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:23.220
Man #3: HEY!
QUIT SCREWING AROUND,

00:03:23.220 --> 00:03:24.586
AND FIGHT LIKE A MAN!

00:03:24.586 --> 00:03:26.253
Nanbu: YEAH, THAT'S IT, JOE.

00:03:26.253 --> 00:03:28.120
HOLD ON TIGHT,
AND DON'T LET HIM GO!

00:03:32.753 --> 00:03:35.286
( crowd laughing )

00:03:35.286 --> 00:03:37.886
Sachio:
I CAN'T WATCH THIS, POPS.

00:03:37.886 --> 00:03:40.320
( Joe panting )

00:03:50.786 --> 00:03:52.120
‐ ( Joe gasps )
‐ ( horn blows )

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:54.220
( crowd cheering )

00:03:58.686 --> 00:04:00.126
( Joe panting )

00:04:03.593 --> 00:04:04.893
Nanbu: GOOD JOB OUT THERE.

00:04:06.093 --> 00:04:08.993
BUT THAT'S ENOUGH.

00:04:08.993 --> 00:04:12.026
EVEN IF YOU GO ALL OUT,
YOU CAN'T WIN THIS FIGHT.

00:04:12.026 --> 00:04:15.093
MAKING SURE HIS BOXER
LEAVES THE RING ALIVE

00:04:15.093 --> 00:04:17.160
IS PART OF A TRAINER'S JOB.

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:19.560
Sachio: WAIT.
YOU WANNA FORFEIT?

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:21.993
Nanbu: LISTEN, JOE,
YOU GOTTA TRUST ME.

00:04:21.993 --> 00:04:24.326
IF WE DON'T STOP NOW,
YOU MIGHT BE HURT TOO BAD

00:04:24.326 --> 00:04:26.026
TO COMPETE
FOR MEGALONIA AGAIN.

00:04:26.026 --> 00:04:27.926
I CAN GET YOU
ANOTHER MATCH IN NO TIME.

00:04:27.926 --> 00:04:29.893
WHAT? AAH!

00:04:29.893 --> 00:04:31.426
LET ME GO.

00:04:31.426 --> 00:04:34.793
Joe: I RECALL YOU SAYING
THIS TRAIN HASN'T GOT ANY STOPS.

00:04:34.793 --> 00:04:35.759
REMEMBER?

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:38.026
Nanbu: YEAH, BUT LISTEN.

00:04:38.026 --> 00:04:41.193
Joe: I'M GOING AS FAR AS I CAN.
TRY TO STOP ME,

00:04:41.193 --> 00:04:43.360
‐ AND YOU'LL BE GETTING OFF.
‐ ( Nanbu groans )

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:45.526
Joe: AND IF YOU
CAN'T DO ANY OF THAT,

00:04:45.526 --> 00:04:48.660
THEN JUST SHUT UP,
AND WATCH WHAT HAPPENS

00:04:48.660 --> 00:04:50.560
( Nanbu groans )

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:52.426
EH? HEY! GIMME THAT!

00:04:52.426 --> 00:04:55.026
Sachio: AFTER ALL,
WE'RE A TEAM, RIGHT?

00:04:55.026 --> 00:04:56.626
Trainer: GREAT WORK.
YOU'VE SET THE PACE.

00:04:56.626 --> 00:04:58.326
‐ Nanbu: SUIT YOURSELF.
‐ Trainer: JUST KEEP IT UP.

00:04:58.326 --> 00:05:01.100
‐ ( horn blowing )
‐ ( Joe grunts )

00:05:03.833 --> 00:05:06.900
SPLIT IT EVENLY, 50‐50.

00:05:06.900 --> 00:05:08.900
Nanbu: HUH? THAT SON OF A...

00:05:10.500 --> 00:05:13.366
NOW THE KID STARTS DOING
WHAT I TOLD HIM TO DO?

00:05:14.966 --> 00:05:16.400
( Aragaki gasps )

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:20.033
Joe: SPLIT IT EVENLY,
FIFTY‐FIFTY.

00:05:20.033 --> 00:05:21.900
( Aragaki gasps )

00:05:21.900 --> 00:05:25.366
WHATEVER. THAT'S NOT
GONNA HELP AGAINST ME.

00:05:30.866 --> 00:05:32.333
( Sachio gasps )

00:05:32.333 --> 00:05:33.900
Referee: HE'S DOWN!

00:05:33.900 --> 00:05:36.133
‐ Computer: ONE, TWO...
‐ Nanbu: LISTEN!

00:05:36.133 --> 00:05:37.800
DON'T WORRY ABOUT
HOW IT'S LOOKIN', JOE!

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:41.366
YOU GOTTA STAY CLOSE TO HIM
SO HIS SPEED WON'T BE A FACTOR.

00:05:41.366 --> 00:05:43.333
IF IT GETS DANGEROUS,
GO AHEAD AND CLINCH!

00:05:43.333 --> 00:05:44.833
JUST HANG IN THERE!

00:05:47.033 --> 00:05:48.300
Joe: YOU'RE THE ONE WHO SAID

00:05:48.300 --> 00:05:50.233
STRATEGY WASN'T
GONNA HELP, POPS.

00:05:50.233 --> 00:05:51.833
( Nanbu growls )

00:05:51.833 --> 00:05:53.633
JOE, DAMN IT.

00:05:53.633 --> 00:05:56.600
WHAT THE HELL IS HE THINKING?!

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:58.033
Sachio: DON'T YOU SEE?

00:05:58.033 --> 00:06:00.840
JOE WANTS TO WIN
USING WHAT YOU TAUGHT HIM.

00:06:02.340 --> 00:06:03.306
( Nanbu grumbles )

00:06:03.306 --> 00:06:05.440
‐ ( horn blows )
‐ ( crowd cheering )

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:07.106
( Joe chuckling )

00:06:13.273 --> 00:06:15.606
Trainer: DON'T WASTE TIME
TOYING WITH HIM.

00:06:15.606 --> 00:06:18.673
FINISH HIM IN THE NEXT ROUND.

00:06:18.673 --> 00:06:20.473
Nanbu: DON'T LEAN
TOO FAR FORWARD.

00:06:20.473 --> 00:06:22.073
NOT TOO FAR BACK, EITHER.

00:06:22.073 --> 00:06:24.940
50‐50. SPLIT YOUR WEIGHT EVENLY.

00:06:24.940 --> 00:06:28.606
THAT'S THE FORM YOU NEED
TO PRACTICE UNTIL IT'S NATURAL.

00:06:28.606 --> 00:06:31.106
Nanbu: SPLIT IT EVENLY, 50‐50.

00:06:31.106 --> 00:06:32.840
( panting )

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:33.840
( Nanbu laughs )

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:35.373
PRETTY ROUGH, ISN'T IT?

00:06:35.373 --> 00:06:38.240
ALMOST MAKES YOU WANNA QUIT
MEGALO‐BOXING, HUH?

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:42.006
YOU SPLIT YOUR WEIGHT
EVENLY, 50‐50.

00:06:42.006 --> 00:06:45.006
NO MATTER HOW TOUGH THINGS
ARE NOW, IF YOU HOLD YOUR FORM,

00:06:45.006 --> 00:06:48.473
TOMORROW WILL BE
WAITING FOR YOU.

00:06:48.473 --> 00:06:53.973
TOMORROW, ARAGAKI. MAKING IT
TO TOMORROW IS ALL YOU NEED.

00:06:53.973 --> 00:06:56.940
Trainer: HEY, ARAGAKI,
ARE YOU LISTENING TO ME?

00:06:56.940 --> 00:06:59.140
( Aragaki chuckles )
YEAH, I'M LISTENING.

00:06:59.140 --> 00:07:01.280
I PUT HIM DOWN
IN THE NEXT ROUND.

00:07:01.280 --> 00:07:02.846
( Joe groans )

00:07:02.846 --> 00:07:05.046
Nanbu: HE'S GOT YOU
COMPLETELY FIGURED OUT, KID.

00:07:05.046 --> 00:07:08.246
PLUS, HE'S GOT THE ADVANTAGE
IN SPEED AND TECHNIQUE.

00:07:08.246 --> 00:07:09.213
YOU CAN'T BEAT HIM.

00:07:09.213 --> 00:07:11.546
IT'S OVER. YOU KNOW IT.

00:07:11.546 --> 00:07:12.980
AT THIS POINT,
ALL HE WANTS TO DO

00:07:12.980 --> 00:07:15.913
IS MAKE SURE I WATCH HIM
BEAT THE LIVIN' HELL OUT OF YOU,

00:07:15.913 --> 00:07:18.280
‐ SO WHY D‐‐
‐ Joe: I'M NOT SO SURE.

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:21.813
AT FIRST,
I THOUGHT THE SAME THING,

00:07:21.813 --> 00:07:23.646
BUT, YOU KNOW...

00:07:25.613 --> 00:07:28.180
THAT MIGHT NOT BE IT.

00:07:30.446 --> 00:07:32.780
Nanbu: HUH? HMM?

00:07:32.780 --> 00:07:34.846
Joe: YEAH, HE'S ON
A COMPLETELY DIFFERENT LEVEL

00:07:34.846 --> 00:07:37.113
THAN THE OTHER GUYS
I'VE FOUGHT,

00:07:37.113 --> 00:07:40.380
BUT I THINK HE'S IN THE RING
FOR THE SAME REASON I AM,

00:07:40.380 --> 00:07:41.646
TO WIN THIS FIGHT.

00:07:44.646 --> 00:07:45.513
( horn blowing )

00:07:45.513 --> 00:07:47.013
AND IF THAT'S THE CASE,

00:07:47.013 --> 00:07:49.146
THERE'S NO WAY IN HELL
I'M GONNA RUN AWAY.

00:07:49.146 --> 00:07:50.613
( Gear clanks )

00:07:52.746 --> 00:07:54.280
Nanbu: ARAGAKI...

00:07:54.280 --> 00:07:56.713
IF THIS ISN'T
ABOUT REVENGE ON ME,

00:07:56.713 --> 00:07:58.813
THEN WHAT THE HELL
IS THIS ABOUT?

00:08:01.220 --> 00:08:03.320
Aragaki: I'VE DECIDED
TO RUIN HIM.

00:08:03.320 --> 00:08:04.820
Nanbu: EH?

00:08:04.820 --> 00:08:05.920
Aragaki: THIS NEW FIGHTER

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:08.153
THAT YOU'VE BEEN
SO CAREFULLY DEVELOPING.

00:08:08.153 --> 00:08:09.553
( Nanbu gasps )

00:08:11.453 --> 00:08:13.086
Joe: WHAT'S WRONG?

00:08:13.086 --> 00:08:15.720
THOSE LEGS LOW ON OIL
OR SOMETHING? ( chuckles )

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:18.420
YOU AIN'T GONNA RUIN ME
LIKE THIS.

00:08:18.420 --> 00:08:19.520
( Aragaki growls )

00:08:21.320 --> 00:08:22.353
( Sachio gasps )

00:08:22.353 --> 00:08:23.786
Nanbu: JOE, I'M SORRY,

00:08:23.786 --> 00:08:25.486
BUT YOU'VE GOT IT WRONG.

00:08:25.486 --> 00:08:27.720
IT WAS A MISTAKE
TO ACCEPT THIS FIGHT.

00:08:29.220 --> 00:08:30.686
( Joe groans )

00:08:30.686 --> 00:08:33.753
Nanbu: NO, LETTING HIM
SHIP OFF TO THAT WAR

00:08:33.753 --> 00:08:35.920
AND NOT BELIEVING
HE'D COME BACK ALIVE,

00:08:35.920 --> 00:08:37.620
THAT'S THE MISTAKE I MADE.

00:08:37.620 --> 00:08:39.320
I WAS WRONG.

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:41.153
I WAS WRONG ABOUT ALL OF IT.

00:08:43.486 --> 00:08:45.586
I'VE BEEN RUNNING FROM IT.

00:08:46.886 --> 00:08:48.086
JOE...

00:08:48.086 --> 00:08:50.853
YOU DON'T NEED TO PAY
FOR WHAT I'VE DONE.

00:09:02.226 --> 00:09:03.226
( crowd cheering )

00:09:03.226 --> 00:09:04.660
Trainer: IT'S OVER.

00:09:04.660 --> 00:09:05.560
Referee: DOWN!

00:09:05.560 --> 00:09:10.426
Computer: ONE, TWO, THREE,

00:09:10.426 --> 00:09:12.993
FOUR, FIVE...

00:09:12.993 --> 00:09:15.860
Nanbu: JOE, ENOUGH! STAY DOWN!

00:09:15.860 --> 00:09:19.893
Computer: SEVEN, EIGHT, NINE...

00:09:24.660 --> 00:09:26.993
Joe: YOU GOT IT ALL WRONG, POPS.

00:09:26.993 --> 00:09:30.426
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN ABOUT
WHAT HAPPENED IN THE PAST.

00:09:30.426 --> 00:09:33.426
THIS GUY'S IN MY WAY,

00:09:33.426 --> 00:09:36.160
SO I'M GONNA BEAT HIM.

00:09:37.426 --> 00:09:39.126
Aragaki: WHY?

00:09:43.893 --> 00:09:44.893
STAY DOWN!

00:09:51.626 --> 00:09:53.460
Joe: SPLIT IT EVENLY, 50‐50.

00:09:53.460 --> 00:09:55.526
Aragaki: HUH? ( growls )

00:09:57.426 --> 00:10:00.533
Joe: SPLIT IT EVENLY, 50‐50.

00:10:00.533 --> 00:10:02.066
Aragaki: SHUT YOUR MOUTH!

00:10:07.833 --> 00:10:10.166
Joe: 50‐50, SPLIT IT EVENLY.

00:10:10.166 --> 00:10:12.200
Aragaki: THAT'S ENOUGH!

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:14.533
SHUT THE HELL UP!

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:29.066
( both gasp )

00:10:29.066 --> 00:10:30.600
‐ ( crowd cheering )
‐ Referee: HE'S DOWN!

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:33.833
( all gasp )

00:10:35.066 --> 00:10:36.866
( Joe chuckles )

00:10:36.866 --> 00:10:42.633
Computer: ONE, TWO, THREE,

00:10:42.633 --> 00:10:45.600
FOUR, FIVE...

00:10:47.266 --> 00:10:47.700
( crowd cheering )

00:10:49.733 --> 00:10:51.133
( crowd cheering )

00:10:53.233 --> 00:10:56.533
Computer: TWO, THREE,

00:10:56.533 --> 00:10:59.100
‐ FOUR...
‐ Sachio: NO WAY. HE DID IT!

00:10:59.100 --> 00:11:01.106
‐ Computer: FIVE...
‐ Trainer: ARAGAKI! GET UP!

00:11:01.106 --> 00:11:03.440
Computer: SIX, SEVEN,

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.906
EIGHT...

00:11:04.906 --> 00:11:06.440
‐ ( Joe chuckles )
‐ ( crowd cheering )

00:11:13.473 --> 00:11:15.406
( Nanbu chuckles )

00:11:17.340 --> 00:11:19.673
I GET IT NOW.

00:11:21.173 --> 00:11:26.073
( horn blows )

00:11:26.073 --> 00:11:27.140
OKAY, BREATHE DEEP.

00:11:27.140 --> 00:11:28.840
( Joe inhales )

00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:31.473
Nanbu: YOU'RE OFF BALANCE
AND LETTING YOUR GUARD DROP.

00:11:31.473 --> 00:11:33.240
IT'S WHEN YOU'RE
WORN OUT LIKE THIS,

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:34.940
YOU GOTTA REMEMBER THE BASICS.

00:11:34.940 --> 00:11:38.173
Joe: SO I'M GUESSING YOU THINK
I'VE GOT A CHANCE NOW?

00:11:38.173 --> 00:11:42.206
Nanbu: YEAH. BET YOUR ASS I DO.

00:11:42.206 --> 00:11:44.206
Trainer:
DON'T LET IT GET TO YOU.

00:11:44.206 --> 00:11:46.240
IT WAS A LUCKY PUNCH.

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:47.473
‐ Aragaki: NO.
‐ Trainer: HMM?

00:11:47.473 --> 00:11:49.606
Aragaki: HE WAS WAITING FOR IT,

00:11:49.606 --> 00:11:52.473
AND HE DIDN'T LET
HIS CHANCE SLIP PAST.

00:11:52.473 --> 00:11:54.840
PLUS HE KEPT UP HIS STANCE
ON TOP OF IT.

00:11:54.840 --> 00:11:56.673
Trainer: MAYBE,
BUT HE'S TOO LATE.

00:11:56.673 --> 00:11:59.473
STUBBORNNESS IS
WHAT KEEPS HIM STANDING.

00:11:59.473 --> 00:12:02.746
GO AFTER HIM. CRUSH HIM.
BREAK HIS SPIRIT.

00:12:04.046 --> 00:12:06.046
( horn blows )

00:12:06.046 --> 00:12:09.246
Nanbu: GOTTA SAY,
THAT KID'S A REAL PIECE OF WORK.

00:12:09.246 --> 00:12:11.313
JOE UNDERSTOOD EVERYTHING.

00:12:11.313 --> 00:12:13.580
HE ACTUALLY UNDERSTOOD IT,

00:12:13.580 --> 00:12:15.580
ALL THE STUFF
HE WAS PRACTICING EVERY DAY,

00:12:15.580 --> 00:12:18.080
BUILDING ONTO HIS CORE,
WOULD EVENTUALLY

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:21.246
BREAK OUT OF ITS SHELL
AND BEAR SOME REAL FRUIT.

00:12:21.246 --> 00:12:23.280
Joe: 50‐50, SPLIT IT EVENLY.

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:35.613
Trainer: KEEP IT UP! THAT'S IT!
YOU'RE WEARIN' HIM DOWN!

00:12:37.380 --> 00:12:38.646
Aragaki: WHY?!

00:12:38.646 --> 00:12:40.713
Nanbu: JOE'S AS DURABLE
AS THEY COME.

00:12:40.713 --> 00:12:43.013
HE MANAGED TO SURVIVE
FIGHT AFTER FIGHT

00:12:43.013 --> 00:12:44.380
IN THE UNDERGROUND RING

00:12:44.380 --> 00:12:46.680
WITH GEAR THAT WAS
BASICALLY USELESS.

00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:49.680
HIS BODY MAY TAKE A BEATING,
BUT HIS SPIRIT WON'T BE BROKEN.

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:53.646
RIGHT NOW, THE KID'S LIKE
A RED‐HOT PIECE OF IRON.

00:12:53.646 --> 00:12:56.546
THE MORE HE'S HIT,
THE TOUGHER HE GETS.

00:12:59.013 --> 00:13:00.286
( clank )

00:13:00.286 --> 00:13:02.320
( Aragaki groans )

00:13:11.220 --> 00:13:13.020
Sachio: WOW, LOOK AT HIM GO!

00:13:13.020 --> 00:13:13.820
( Nanbu gasps )

00:13:18.753 --> 00:13:21.453
( Joe chuckles )

00:13:24.520 --> 00:13:28.386
Nanbu: WE'RE DOING THIS
FOR TOMORROW, ARAGAKI.

00:13:30.386 --> 00:13:33.220
Trainer: THIS MATCH IS
JUST SO YOU CAN MOVE UP.

00:13:33.220 --> 00:13:35.353
YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

00:13:35.353 --> 00:13:36.986
‐ ARAGAKI!
‐ ( Aragaki gasps )

00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:41.786
‐ ( clanks )
‐ ( groans )

00:13:49.086 --> 00:13:50.686
Man: GO! GET HIM!

