( Joe sighs )

00:14:36.926 --> 00:14:37.726
( Aragaki sighs )

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:45.826
Nanbu: DOES IT HURT?

00:14:45.826 --> 00:14:48.326
( Joe winces )
NOT ENOUGH TO BOTHER ME.

00:14:48.326 --> 00:14:50.360
Man #2: FIGHT ALREADY! COME ON!

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:52.560
Aragaki: FOR TOMORROW...

00:14:52.560 --> 00:14:54.860
‐ Trainer: HUH?
‐ Aragaki: RIGHT?

00:14:54.860 --> 00:14:56.460
( sighs )

00:14:57.826 --> 00:14:59.566
COACH MIYAGI...

00:15:03.366 --> 00:15:05.566
‐ ( horn blowing )
‐ Nanbu: OKAY.

00:15:06.866 --> 00:15:08.233
( all gasp )

00:15:10.166 --> 00:15:11.533
( crowd murmuring )

00:15:11.533 --> 00:15:13.433
Man #3: COME ON.
I GOT MONEY ON THIS.

00:15:13.433 --> 00:15:15.500
Man #4: LET'S GO. FIGHT.

00:15:16.766 --> 00:15:18.533
Nanbu: HUH?

00:15:18.533 --> 00:15:20.966
Woman: GET UP, ALREADY.
COME ON! LET'S FIGHT!

00:15:20.966 --> 00:15:22.366
( horn blowing )

00:15:22.366 --> 00:15:24.000
Referee: ARAGAKI HAS
FORFEITED THE MATCH.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:27.733
WINNER BY TKO AT THE CONCLUSION
OF THE FOURTH ROUND IS...

00:15:27.733 --> 00:15:30.066
"GEARLESS" JOE!

00:15:30.066 --> 00:15:32.433
( crowd cheering )

00:15:34.433 --> 00:15:36.166
Sachio: DID WE WIN?

00:15:36.166 --> 00:15:38.033
Nanbu: YEAH.

00:15:38.033 --> 00:15:39.000
Sachio: JOE!

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:41.300
WE WON! WE WON!

00:15:41.300 --> 00:15:44.233
JOE, WE WON THE FIGHT!

00:15:44.233 --> 00:15:46.033
‐ Joe: WE WON?
‐ Sachio: WHOO‐HOO!

00:15:46.033 --> 00:15:48.666
‐ ( Joe chuckles )
‐ Sachio: YOU'RE AMAZING, JOE!

00:15:48.666 --> 00:15:50.500
‐ Joe: WE DID IT.
‐ Man #5: "GEARLESS" JOE!

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:52.333
‐ Nanbu: AHH!
‐ Man #6: "GEARLESS" JOE!

00:15:52.333 --> 00:15:54.433
ARAGAKI, WAY TO GO!

00:16:06.140 --> 00:16:07.473
( leg scraping )

00:16:07.473 --> 00:16:08.806
Aragaki: I'M SORRY, COACH.

00:16:08.806 --> 00:16:12.173
‐ Miyagi: NO NEED TO APOLOGIZE.
‐ Aragaki: HUH?

00:16:12.173 --> 00:16:14.340
Miyagi: DID YOU THINK
I HADN'T NOTICED?

00:16:14.340 --> 00:16:16.773
IF YOU HADN'T SPOKEN UP,

00:16:16.773 --> 00:16:20.173
THEN I WAS GONNA STOP
THE FIGHT MYSELF.

00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:24.273
LISTEN. I'M YOUR TRAINER.

00:16:24.273 --> 00:16:25.673
THE LAST THING I WANT

00:16:25.673 --> 00:16:28.706
IS FOR MY FIGHTER
NEVER TO BE ABLE TO WALK AGAIN.

00:16:31.006 --> 00:16:33.440
THERE'S NOTHING
TO BE ASHAMED OF.

00:16:33.440 --> 00:16:36.173
THAT WAS A HELL OF A FIGHT
TO GO OUT ON.

00:16:42.806 --> 00:16:44.340
( door opens )

00:16:44.340 --> 00:16:46.073
Aragaki: YOU CAME.

00:16:46.073 --> 00:16:47.706
EVERYBODY, CLEAR OUT.

00:16:50.640 --> 00:16:52.340
Nanbu: I APPRECIATE IT.

00:16:52.340 --> 00:16:53.706
Aragaki: NO PROBLEM.

00:17:08.246 --> 00:17:10.680
Nanbu: SO YOU WERE INJURED.

00:17:10.680 --> 00:17:14.246
Aragaki: YEAH. THE DOCTORS SAID
I RISKED BEING BEDRIDDEN

00:17:14.246 --> 00:17:17.746
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE
BY PUSHING IT SO HARD OUT THERE,

00:17:17.746 --> 00:17:20.446
BUT I HAD A DIFFICULT TIME
LETTING GO.

00:17:21.813 --> 00:17:24.680
WHEN I HEARD ABOUT
WHAT YOU AND JOE WERE DOING,

00:17:24.680 --> 00:17:27.680
I THOUGHT IT'D BE
A GOOD WAY TO GO OUT

00:17:27.680 --> 00:17:31.546
FOR ALL OF IT,
AN END TO EVERYTHING.

00:17:31.546 --> 00:17:35.313
BUT THEN,
WHEN I ACTUALLY SAW YOU AGAIN

00:17:35.313 --> 00:17:38.046
AFTER ALL THOSE YEARS APART,

00:17:38.046 --> 00:17:40.646
I WASN'T SURE
WHAT I WANTED TO DO.

00:17:40.646 --> 00:17:43.580
I HAVE BEEN TRYING
TO FIGURE THAT ALL OUT

00:17:43.580 --> 00:17:46.980
SINCE THAT DAY
WE SPOKE IN THE PARK.

00:17:46.980 --> 00:17:49.313
Nanbu: AND DID YOU?

00:17:49.313 --> 00:17:50.680
( Aragaki chuckles )

00:17:50.680 --> 00:17:53.613
JOE TOLD ME SOMETHING.

00:17:53.613 --> 00:17:55.446
"BLAME WHOEVER YOU WANT,

00:17:55.446 --> 00:17:58.546
BUT IN THE END,
A MAN MAKES HIS OWN CALLS."

00:17:58.546 --> 00:18:01.720
I CHOSE THE PATH
THAT LED ME HERE.

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:04.120
I CAN'T RESENT ANYONE FOR THAT.

00:18:04.120 --> 00:18:07.053
THAT INCLUDES YOU.

00:18:07.053 --> 00:18:09.653
I HOLD NO ILL WILL.

00:18:12.853 --> 00:18:15.020
I'M GONNA MOVE ON.

00:18:15.020 --> 00:18:19.920
FOR ME, TOMORROW STARTS TODAY.

00:18:19.920 --> 00:18:21.920
♪

00:18:21.920 --> 00:18:25.153
I MADE IT THIS FAR
ON THESE LEGS...

00:18:26.653 --> 00:18:29.053
AND THAT'S‐‐
THAT SHOULD BE FAR ENOUGH,

00:18:29.053 --> 00:18:32.020
SHOULDN'T IT, COACH?

00:18:32.020 --> 00:18:34.020
Nanbu: YEAH.

00:18:34.020 --> 00:18:36.953
IT WAS GOOD TO SEE
YOUR MEGALO‐BOXING.

00:18:36.953 --> 00:18:39.186
YOU WERE AMAZING.

00:18:39.186 --> 00:18:40.620
( Aragaki shudders )

00:18:43.086 --> 00:18:44.086
WOULD YOU MIND...

00:18:44.086 --> 00:18:46.253
GIVING THIS TO JOE FOR ME?

00:18:50.053 --> 00:18:54.386
Nanbu: YOU‐‐YOU HELD ON TO THIS?

00:18:57.220 --> 00:18:59.053
( Aragaki sighs )

00:18:59.053 --> 00:19:02.360
I, UH‐‐I SHIP OUT TOMORROW.

00:19:02.360 --> 00:19:03.893
Nanbu: I SEE.

00:19:06.226 --> 00:19:07.526
HERE.

00:19:07.526 --> 00:19:09.293
Aragaki: WHAT IS THIS?

00:19:09.293 --> 00:19:11.426
Nanbu: ARAGAKI,
I WAS HOPING TO TREAT YOU

00:19:11.426 --> 00:19:13.826
TO A NICE DINNER
BEFORE YOU SHIPPED OUT,

00:19:13.826 --> 00:19:16.726
SO I BET ALL THE CASH I HAD,
HOPING FOR AN UPSET.

00:19:16.726 --> 00:19:20.193
BUT GUESS WHAT. I LOST IT ALL.

00:19:20.193 --> 00:19:23.093
THINK OF IT
AS A GOOD‐LUCK CHARM.

00:19:23.093 --> 00:19:27.260
HOPEFULLY IT'LL KEEP YOU
FROM GETTING SHOT.

00:19:28.526 --> 00:19:30.826
LEAVE YOUR LOCKER
THE WAY IT IS.

00:19:30.826 --> 00:19:32.093
THIS IS YOUR HOME.

00:19:32.093 --> 00:19:34.126
REMEMBER THAT, OKAY?

00:19:34.126 --> 00:19:36.826
I'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU.

00:19:36.826 --> 00:19:38.026
Aragaki: RIGHT.

00:19:38.026 --> 00:19:40.060
THAT TICKET...

00:19:40.060 --> 00:19:42.693
HONESTLY, IT SAVED MY LIFE.

00:19:42.693 --> 00:19:44.426
( sobbing )

00:19:50.460 --> 00:19:52.326
( wailing )

00:19:55.960 --> 00:19:57.793
YOU'LL MAKE IT
TO MEGALONIA, RIGHT?

00:19:57.793 --> 00:19:58.560
Nanbu: EH?

00:20:06.566 --> 00:20:07.866
YEAH.

00:20:07.866 --> 00:20:10.533
Aragaki: TELL JOE
SOMETHING FOR ME.

00:20:10.533 --> 00:20:12.866
TELL HIM I BELIEVE IN HIM, TOO.

00:20:12.866 --> 00:20:14.900
( Joe inhales )

00:20:14.900 --> 00:20:16.033
( sighs )

00:20:16.033 --> 00:20:18.100
( crowd cheering )

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:27.566
( fanfare playing )

00:20:27.566 --> 00:20:30.566
Yukiko: TONIGHT WE'LL BE
ANNOUNCING THE THIRD COMPETITOR

00:20:30.566 --> 00:20:33.966
TO GAIN ENTRY
INTO THE MEGALONIA TOURNAMENT.

00:20:33.966 --> 00:20:38.633
YURI, PEPE IGLESIAS, AND NOW...

00:20:38.633 --> 00:20:40.100
( lion roars )

00:20:41.900 --> 00:20:44.366
Announcer:
WITH THE KILLER BOMB CREW...

00:20:44.366 --> 00:20:47.466
GLEN BURROUGHS!

00:20:47.466 --> 00:20:50.000
( audience murmuring )

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:52.433
Yukiko: MR. BURROUGHS'S
THUNDEROUS FIGHTING STYLE

00:20:52.433 --> 00:20:54.900
IS A SIGHT TO BEHOLD,
AND IT'S EARNED HIM

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:57.400
THE INFAMOUS NICKNAME
OF "BLOODY LION."

00:20:57.400 --> 00:20:59.200
THIS POWERFUL
HEAVYWEIGHT FIGHTER

00:20:59.200 --> 00:21:02.140
HAS MANAGED TO DISTINGUISH
HIMSELF IN MEGALO‐BOXING,

00:21:02.140 --> 00:21:04.640
WHERE MIDDLEWEIGHT FIGHTERS
TYPICALLY HAVE THE ADVANTAGE.

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:07.773
Announcer: LET'S GIVE IT UP
FOR GLEN BURROUGHS!

00:21:07.773 --> 00:21:10.606
( applause )

00:21:10.606 --> 00:21:14.006
Reporter: THERE'S LESS THAN
A MONTH UNTIL MEGALONIA BEGINS.

00:21:14.006 --> 00:21:15.973
WHEN WILL THE LAST FIGHTER
BE ANNOUNCED,

00:21:15.973 --> 00:21:17.740
AND WHAT WILL THE CRITERIA BE?

00:21:17.740 --> 00:21:19.806
Yukiko:
AFTER A COMPREHENSIVE REVIEW,

00:21:19.806 --> 00:21:22.206
WE'LL PUBLICLY ANNOUNCE
THAT COMPETITOR.

00:21:22.206 --> 00:21:23.206
Reporter #2:
WHAT ARE THE CHANCES

00:21:23.206 --> 00:21:25.006
OF "GEARLESS" JOE ENTERING?

00:21:25.006 --> 00:21:26.806
HE RECENTLY DEFEATED ARAGAKI,

00:21:26.806 --> 00:21:28.773
A FAVORITE
TO CLAIM THE LAST SLOT.

00:21:28.773 --> 00:21:30.506
Yukiko: WELL...

00:21:30.506 --> 00:21:33.473
AS I'VE SAID BEFORE,
MEGALONIA IS OPEN TO ALL.

00:21:33.473 --> 00:21:36.840
I ASSURE YOU, ONCE THE LAST
FIGHTER HAS BEEN SELECTED,

00:21:36.840 --> 00:21:38.340
YOU WILL ALL BE INFORMED.

00:21:40.773 --> 00:21:42.740
Mikio: YOU LOOK BORED
OUT HERE, YURI.

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:45.873
Yuri: MIKIO.

00:21:45.873 --> 00:21:47.973
Mikio: TOUGH LUCK
FOR MR. BURROUGHS.

00:21:47.973 --> 00:21:50.773
INSTEAD OF GETTING
HIS MOMENT IN THE SPOTLIGHT,

00:21:50.773 --> 00:21:53.273
THE MEDIA FOCUSED
ON SOMEONE ELSE.

00:21:53.273 --> 00:21:54.206
Yuri: HMM?

00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:08.413
HE'S DOING IT.

00:22:08.413 --> 00:22:10.580
Mikio: YUKIKO TOLD ME
ALL ABOUT IT.

00:22:10.580 --> 00:22:14.346
IT SEEMS LIKE YOU TWO
HAVE SOME UNFINISHED BUSINESS,

00:22:14.346 --> 00:22:17.780
THE MYSTERY FIGHTER
WHO MEGALOBOXES

00:22:17.780 --> 00:22:21.746
WITHOUT ANY ENHANCEMENTS,
"GEARLESS" JOE.

00:22:21.746 --> 00:22:24.146
HE'S QUITE POPULAR.

00:22:24.146 --> 00:22:25.746
Yuri: JOE.

00:22:27.446 --> 00:22:30.413
Mikio: BUT THAT WILL SOON
COME TO AN END.

00:22:30.413 --> 00:22:35.180
MEGALONIA IS NO PLACE
FOR STRAY DOGS LIKE HIM.

